\c 29
\s Vanhu vanouya nezvipo zvekuvaka tembere nazvo
\p
\v 1 Zvino mambo Dhavhidhi wakati kuungano yese: Mwanakomana wangu Soromoni, uyo Jehovha waakasarudza mudiki \add uye\add* haana simba, zvino basa iguru; nokuti muzinda hausi wemunhu asi waJehovha Mwari.
\v 2 Zvino ndagadzirira nesimba rangu rese imba yaMwari wangu, goridhe rezvegoridhe, nesirivha yezvesirivha, nendarira yezvendarira, nematare ezvematare, nematanda ezvematanda; mabwe eonikisi neekuiswa, mabwe anopenya neemavara-mavara, nemamdo dzese dzemabwe anokosha, nemabwe earabhasiteri* muuwandu.
\v 3 Uyezve, nekuda kwekuda kwangu imba yaMwari wangu, fuma ndinayo pachangu, fuma yegoridhe nesirivha ndinopa imba yaMwari wangu, pamusoro pezvese zvandakagadzirira nzvimbo;
\v 4 matarenda* egoridhe zvuru zvitatu, egoridhe reOfiri, nematarenda akanatswa esirivha zvuru zvinomwe, kudzudzura madziro eimba \add nazvo.\add*
\v 5 Goridhe rezvegoridhe, nesirivha yezvesirivha, nezvemabasa emarudzi ese basa remaoko emhizha. Zvino ndiani anoda kunatsira ruoko rwake Jehovha nhasi?
\p
\v 6 Zvino misoro yemadzibaba, nemisoro yemarudzi aIsraeri, nemisoro yezvuru neyemazana, nemisoro yevebasa ramambo vakapa nechido.
\v 7 Zvino vakapa pabasa reimba yaMwari, pagoridhe matarenda zvuru zvishanu, nemakobiri zvuru gumi, uye pasirivha matarenda zvuru gumi, nepandarira, matarenda zvuru gumi nezvisere, nematare matarenda zvuru zana.
\v 8 Neavo kwakawanikwa kwavari zvibwe, vakaapa kufuma yeimba yaJehovha neruoko rwaJehieri muGerishoni.
\v 9 Zvino vanhu vakafara nekupa kwavo nechido, nokuti nemoyo wakaperera vakapa nechido kuna Jehovha, namambo Dhavhidhiwo vakafarawo, mufaro mukuru.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Dhavhidhi wakarumbidza Jehovha pamberi peungano yese; Dhavhidhi ndokuti: Rumbidzwai imwi Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri baba vedu kubva rinhi narinhi kusvika rinhi narinhi.
\v 11 Ndezvenyu Jehovha, ukuru nesimba nekubwinya nekukunda neumambo, nokuti zvese zviri kudenga nezviri pasi \add ndezvenyu\add*; ushe ndehwenyu, Jehovha, uye makakudzwa mukava musoro wezvese.
\v 12 Zvese fuma nerukudzo zvinobva kwamuri, uye imwi munotonga pamusoro pezvese; uye muruoko rwenyu mune kugwinya nesimba, ruoko rwenyu rwunokurisa nekupa vese simba.
\v 13 Naizvozvo zvino Mwari wedu, tinopa kuvonga kwamuri uye tinopa rumbidzo kuzita renyu rakanakisisa.
\v 14 Zvino ini ndini ani, nevanhu vangu chinyii, kuti tigone kupa nechido zvakadai, nokuti zvese zvinobva kwamuri, uye tapa kwamuri zvinobva paruoko rwenyu.
\v 15 Nokuti tiri vaenzi pamberi penyu nevatorwa, semadzibaba edu ese; mazuva edu panyika akaita semumvuri, uye hakuna tariro.
\v 16 Jehovha Mwari wedu, zvakawanda zvese izvi zvatakagadzira kukuvakirai imba yezita renyu dzvene, zvinobva paruoko rwenyu; uye zvese ndezvenyu.
\v 17 Ndinozivawo Mwari wangu, kuti imwi munonzvera moyo, uye munofanira kurarama. Kana ndiri ini, mukururama kwemoyo wangu, ndakapa izvi zvese nechido, uye ikozvino ndaona vanhu venyu nemufaro ivo vanowanikwa pano kuti vape nechido kwamuri.
\v 18 Haiwa Jehovha Mwari waAbhurahama, Isaka, naIsraeri, madzibaba edu, chengetai izvi kusvika rinhi narinhi mundangariro dzemifungo yemoyo yevanhu venyu, uye mugadzirire moyo wavo kwamuri.
\v 19 Zvino ipai Soromoni mwanakomana wangu moyo wakaperera, kuchengeta mirairo yenyu, zvipupuro zvenyu, nezvimiso zvenyu uye kuita zvese nekuvaka muzinda wandagadzirira.
\p
\v 20 Dhavhidhi ndokuti kuungano yese: Zvino rumbidzai Jehovha Mwari wenyu. Ungano yese ndokurumbidza Jehovha Mwari wemadzibaba avo, ndokukotamisa misoro yavo, ndokushumira Jehovha namambo.
\v 21 Zvino vakabaira zvibairo kuna Jehovha, ndokupa zvipo zvinopiswa kuna Jehovha chifume chezuva iro: Nzombe diki churu chimwe, makondohwe chiuru chimwe, makwaiana ane chiuru chimwe, pamwe chete nezvipo zvazvo zvinodururwa, nezvibairo zvakawanda zvaVaIsraeri vese;
\v 22 vakadya, vakanwa pamberi paJehovha nomufaro mukuru nezuva iro. Vakaita Soromoni mwanakomana waDhavhidhi mambo rwechipiri, vakamuzodzera Jehovha ave mutungamiriri, naZadhoki ave mupristi.
\v 23 Ipapo Soromoni akagara pachigaro choushe chaJehovha akava mambo panzvimbo yaDhavhidhi baba vake, akafambiswa zvakanaka; VaIsraeri vese vakamuteerera.
\v 24 Machinda ese, navanhu vese vane simba, navanakomana vese vamambo Dhavhidhi vakazviisa pasi pamambo Soromoni.
\v 25 Jehovha akakudza Soromoni kwazvo-kwazvo pamberi paVaIsraeri vese, akamupa umambo hwakakura, husina kumbopiwa umwe mambo waIsraeri wakamutangira.
\s Kufa kwaDhavhidhi
\p
\v 26 Zvino Dhavhidhi mwanakomana waJese akabata VaIsraeri vese paushe hwake.
\v 27 Nguva yaakabata ushe hwaIsraeri aiva makore makumi mana; wakabata ushe paHebhuroni makore manomwe, napaJerusarema akabata ushe makore makumi matatu namatatu.
\v 28 Akazofa akwegura kwazvo, ava namakore mazhinji, nefuma, nokukudzwa; Soromoni mwanakomana wake akabata ushe panzvimbo yake.
\v 29 Zvino mabasa amambo Dhavhidhi, okutanga nookupedzisira, tarirai, akanyorwa pamashoko omuoni Samueri, napamashoko omupristi Natani, napamashoko omuoni Gadhi;
\v 30 pamwe chete namashoko oushe hwake, nesimba rake, nezvaakaitirwa panguva dzese, iye naVaIsraeri, noushe hwese hwedzimwe nyika.
